data.description:
Check out this gem in a tranquil country setting!!!
    This home has 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with a remarkable workshop. The workshop designed and thoughtfully appointed, 1-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment, offering a haven for guests or the potential for rental income.
    The recent conversion from a 3-bedroom to a 2-bedroom layout was done, allowing for the creation of a spacious master closet. However, should the need arise, the configuration can easily be reverted to accommodate a third bedroom.
This home sits on an extensive 5 acres lot allowing a place to put a garden or have livestock. It also offers a large back deck with an above ground swimming pool perfect for cooling off during the heated months. If this sounds like a place you would like to call home, reach out today!!!
